data.title: WESM Participant Handbook Vol1 Ver2
data.meta_description: WESM Participant Handbook Vol1 Ver2 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides an overview of the registration process for the Philippine Wholesale Electricity Spot Market (WESM). There are different categories of WESM membership including direct members, indirect members, and intending members. Direct members such as generators and customers can trade directly in the WESM, while indirect members trade through a direct member. The summary outlines the key registration requirements for each category of member such as completing application forms, providing licenses and certificates, and signing participation agreements. Training programs are also available to help participants understand market fundamentals and operations.
